      <description>&lt;script src=&#34;https://www.dustysturner.com/post/2018-12-27-analysis-of-my-children-s-reading-list/index_files/htmlwidgets/htmlwidgets.js&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;script src=&#34;https://www.dustysturner.com/post/2018-12-27-analysis-of-my-children-s-reading-list/index_files/jquery/jquery.min.js&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;link href=&#34;https://www.dustysturner.com/post/2018-12-27-analysis-of-my-children-s-reading-list/index_files/datatables-css/datatables-crosstalk.css&#34; rel=&#34;stylesheet&#34; /&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;script src=&#34;https://www.dustysturner.com/post/2018-12-27-analysis-of-my-children-s-reading-list/index_files/datatables-binding/datatables.js&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;link href=&#34;https://www.dustysturner.com/post/2018-12-27-analysis-of-my-children-s-reading-list/index_files/dt-core/css/jquery.dataTables.min.css&#34; rel=&#34;stylesheet&#34; /&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;link href=&#34;https://www.dustysturner.com/post/2018-12-27-analysis-of-my-children-s-reading-list/index_files/dt-core/css/jquery.dataTables.extra.css&#34; rel=&#34;stylesheet&#34; /&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;script src=&#34;https://www.dustysturner.com/post/2018-12-27-analysis-of-my-children-s-reading-list/index_files/dt-core/js/jquery.dataTables.min.js&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;link href=&#34;https://www.dustysturner.com/post/2018-12-27-analysis-of-my-children-s-reading-list/index_files/crosstalk/css/crosstalk.css&#34; rel=&#34;stylesheet&#34; /&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;script src=&#34;https://www.dustysturner.com/post/2018-12-27-analysis-of-my-children-s-reading-list/index_files/crosstalk/js/crosstalk.min.js&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;introduction&#34; class=&#34;section level2&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2&gt;Introduction&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Over Christmas 2017, my wife, &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.instagram.com/jillturner117/&#34;&gt;Jill&lt;/a&gt;, resolved that our family (to include babysitters) would read our children over 1000 new books in 2018. More specifically, 29 December 2017 - 28 December 2018.&lt;/p&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A goal like this takes dedication, love, and of course, a Data Science-y approach.&lt;/p&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Special thanks to Ally, Zia, and &lt;a href=&#34;https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/bookbuddy-pro-library-manager/id395149950?mt=8&#34;&gt;Bookbuddy&lt;/a&gt; for help in accomplishing this goal!&lt;/p&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Also, special thanks to &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/drob&#34;&gt;drob&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/juliasilge&#34;&gt;juliasilge&lt;/a&gt; who privde the &lt;code&gt;tidytext&lt;/code&gt; package and the entire R open-source community I rely on to do this analysis.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
